These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, mirinda, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the van is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person driving the trike and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Beverage         | iced-tea    | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate       | mirinda     |
| Transport   | trike     | jet-ski | van       | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, d&b, techno, funk
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
4. the fan of funk is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of d&b##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | funk | electronic | techno      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, september, july
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, house, indie
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of indie and the person who's birthday is in june##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | june | july         | october   | september    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | house   | folk        | indie      | country   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, polish
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, architect, police-officer, bartender
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the polish##2
3. the german is on the right of the architect##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the police-officer##1
5. the german is on the right of the australian##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the librarian and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | polish        | dutch   | australian | german |
| Job         | police-officer | librarian | architect    | bartender |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

