.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, january, november
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday         | november  | february | january | september |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | western | crime   | spy         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

