The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, march, october
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Birthday        | october  | july      | march        | june      |

