.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, black, light-blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes black is between the person drinking tea and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | mirinda | tea           | soy-milk |
| Color       | chestnut | black    | blue          | light-blue   |
| Sport      | swimming  | rugby   | weightlifting | cricket  |

