3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the ritmeester-smoker and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Cigar      | dunhill | oliveros | ritmeester     | baccarat   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

